            <lg xml:id="TK1186">
<l>viḷakkaṟṟam pārkku miruḷēpōṟ koṇkaṉ </l>
<l> muyakkaṟṟam pārkkum pacappu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Just as darkness waits for the failing light; so does sallowness wait for the laxity of my husband's intercourse.</l>
